	<content><![CDATA[

Fragmentation is a breaking a packet into smaller pieces (fragment). a packet is fragmented, when the packet is larger than the MTU. 

when we do the fragmentation, each small packet will have the same source and destiation ip address. These small packets are collected and reassembled by the destination.


]]></content>
